MESSAGES.FILL-PARAMETER: Fill in the parameters to generate your report

PROCESS-DEFINITION-OVERVIEW.GENERAL-TABLE-ACTIVE-PROCESS-INSTANCES: Total number of active process instances
PROCESS-DEFINITION-OVERVIEW.GENERAL-TABLE-COMPLETED-PROCESS-INSTANCE: Total number of completed process instances

PROCESS-HEAT-MAP.TYPE-FILTERING: Include all process steps (Unchecking this, will remove pass through steps like start events, gateways, etc.)?

PROCESS-INSTANCES-OVERVIEW.SLOW-PROC-INST-NUMBER: How many of the slowest process instances should be displayed?

TASK-SLA.SLA-DURATION: What is the time this task needs to be completed in to be within the SLA?

DIALOG.SAVE_MESSAGE: The current parameter settings will be stored, and a new report will be shown in the reports list. When that particular report is clicked, the report will be generated using these saved parameter values.

MESSAGES.START-LESS-THAN-END-DATE: Start date must be less than End date
